Description:
    Creates Node.js HTTP and WebSocket servers with security baked in

Options:
    HTTP server port?
        Choose HTTP server port
    WebSocket server port?
        Choose WebSocket server port

Example:
    yo techtonic:server

        This will create:
            package.json          - Development packages installed by npm
            app.json              - Configuration file for deploying to Heroku
            index.js              - Server entry point
            web/server.js         - HTTP server module
            web/socket.js         - WebSocket server module
            web/client/index.html - Default client entry point
